---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="No One Has Altitude Over You - Be More Free">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative py-24 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 via-white to-accent-50"></div>
    
    <!-- Decorative elements -->
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-96 h-96 bg-gradient-to-bl from-accent-200/20 to-transparent rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-96 h-96 bg-gradient-to-tr from-primary-200/20 to-transparent rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
    
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <div class="text-6xl mb-6">üéØ</div>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-8 leading-tight">
          No One Has <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-accent-500">Altitude</span> Over You
        </h1>
        <p class="text-2xl text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          The facilitator doesn't evaluate, interpret, judge, or direct. You explore what YOU want to explore.
        </p>
        <nav class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700 transition-colors">
          <a href="/booking/free-trial" class="inline-flex items-center">
            ‚Üê Back 
          </a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">
      <!-- Core Principle -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-black mb-8 text-gray-900">
          What Does "No Altitude" Mean?
        </h2>
        
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 to-accent-50 rounded-2xl p-8 mb-8">
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            In most therapeutic or coaching relationships, there's an implicit hierarchy. The professional 
            is positioned as the expert who knows better than you about your own experience. They evaluate 
            your thoughts, interpret your words, and guide you toward their understanding of what you need.
          </p>
          
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            In the Neutral Zone, this dynamic doesn't exist. The facilitator has no altitude over you‚Äîno 
            superior position from which to judge, direct, or interpret. You are the expert on your own experience.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- How This is Different -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-gray-900">
          How This Differs from Traditional Approaches
        </h3>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-red-50 to-orange-50 border border-red-200 rounded-xl p-6">
            <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-red-900 flex items-center">
              <span class="text-red-500 mr-3 text-2xl">‚úó</span>
              Traditional Approach
            </h4>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
              <li>"I think what you really mean is..."</li>
              <li>"Have you considered that this might be about..."</li>
              <li>"Let me help you understand what's happening"</li>
              <li>"Based on my experience, you should..."</li>
              <li>"This sounds like a pattern of..."</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-green-50 to-emerald-50 border border-green-200 rounded-xl p-6">
            <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-green-900 flex items-center">
              <span class="text-green-500 mr-3 text-2xl">‚úì</span>
              Neutral Zone Approach
            </h4>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
              <li>"What would you like to look at today?"</li>
              <li>"What would you call that (something that's bothering you today)?"</li>
              <li>"How does that feel to you?"</li>
              <li>"Is that something you should look at today?"</li>
              <li>Complete acceptance of your direction</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- What This Means for You -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-gray-900">
          What This Means for Your Session
        </h3>
        
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="bg-white border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-primary-300 transition-colors">
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
              <span class="text-3xl">üß≠</span>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">You Set the Direction</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                  Want to explore a fear or dread? A work situation? Some recurring issue in life? Something from your past? 
                  The choice is entirely yours. No agenda is imposed.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-primary-300 transition-colors">
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
              <span class="text-3xl">üö´</span>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">No Evaluation or Judgment</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                  Your thoughts, feelings, and experiences aren't categorized as healthy/unhealthy, 
                  right/wrong, or productive/unproductive. They're simply what's there.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-primary-300 transition-colors">
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
              <span class="text-3xl">üéØ</span>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Your Pace, Your Depth</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                  Whether you want to stay on the surface or dive deep, whether you want to 
                  explore for 5 minutes or the full session‚Äîit's up to you.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-primary-300 transition-colors">
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
              <span class="text-3xl">üí°</span>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Your Insights Are Valid</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                  When you have a realization or insight, it's not filtered through someone 
                  else's theoretical framework. Your understanding stands on its own.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Why This Matters -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-gray-900">
          Why This Creates Real Change
        </h3>
        
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-50 to-orange-50 border-2 border-amber-300 rounded-2xl p-8">
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            When no one has altitude over you, something remarkable happens: you stop performing for 
            an external authority and start exploring authentically. You're not trying to give the 
            "right" answer or meet someone else's expectations.
          </p>
          
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            This authentic exploration allows you to encounter material you might never access when 
            you're being guided, evaluated, or interpreted. Your own wisdom emerges when it's given 
            genuine space to do so.
          </p>
          
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            The changes that come from this kind of authentic exploration tend to be lasting because 
            they come from you‚Äînot from someone else's understanding of what you need.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Related Principles -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-8 text-center text-gray-900">
        Other Neutral Zone Principles
      </h3>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <a href="/principles/truth" class="bg-white rounded-xl p-4 border border-gray-200 hover:border-primary-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-all group">
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
            <span class="text-2xl">üíØ</span>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold group-hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors">Everything You Say is Truth</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Your experience is valid, period</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>
        
        <a href="/principles/hours-not-years" class="bg-white rounded-xl p-4 border border-gray-200 hover:border-primary-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-all group">
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
            <span class="text-2xl">‚ö°</span>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold group-hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors">Hours, Not Years</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Address what's actually there</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>
        
        <a href="/principles/find-answers" class="bg-white rounded-xl p-4 border border-gray-200 hover:border-primary-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-all group">
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
            <span class="text-2xl">üß≠</span>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold group-hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors">Find Your Own Answers</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Your wisdom emerges with space</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>
        
        <a href="/principles/complete-acceptance" class="bg-white rounded-xl p-4 border border-gray-200 hover:border-primary-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-all group">
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
            <span class="text-2xl">ü§ù</span>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold group-hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors">Complete Acceptance</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Examine all parts without judgment</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>
        
        <a href="/principles/no-prerequisites" class="bg-white rounded-xl p-4 border border-gray-200 hover:border-primary-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-all group">
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
            <span class="text-2xl">üöÄ</span>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold group-hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors">No Prerequisites</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Just start looking</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-24 relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-600 via-primary-700 to-accent-600"></div>
    
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center relative z-10">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mb-6">
        Experience What "No Altitude" Feels Like
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-white/90 mb-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Your first 30-minute Neutral Zone session is free. Discover what happens 
        when you're truly the expert on your own experience.
      </p>
      <a href="/booking/free-trial" 
         class="group bg-white text-primary-700 px-12 py-6 rounded-full text-xl font-bold hover:bg-accent-400 hover:text-white transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 shadow-2xl inline-flex items-center">
        Book Your Free Trial Session
        <span class="ml-3 group-hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform">‚Üí</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
